{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be secure and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Secure Design Agency</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #c0392b; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #e74c3c; /* Lighter red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #2c3e50; /* Dark blue-grey */\n            --hover-color: #922b21; /* Darker red */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--hover-color);\n        }\n\n        main {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            -webkit-background-clip: text;\n            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n            color: transparent; /* Fallback for browsers not supporting background-clip */\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .services-section, .contact-section {\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            width: 100%;\n        }\n\n        .services-section h2, .contact-section h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-section p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-section a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: underline;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-section a:hover {\n            color: var(--hover-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: auto;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        /* Security specific styles */\n        body::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\"><polygon points=\"0,0 100,0 100,100 0,100\" fill=\"%23f0f0f0\" opacity=\"0.05\"/><path d=\"M50 10 L90 30 L90 70 L50 90 L10 70 L10 30 Z\" stroke=\"%23c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" opacity=\"0.3\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"30\" stroke=\"%23c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" opacity=\"0.3\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"10\" x2=\"90\" y2=\"30\" stroke=\"%23c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" opacity=\"0.3\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"10\" y2=\"70\" stroke=\"%23c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" opacity=\"0.3\"/><line x1=\"90\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"90\" y2=\"70\" stroke=\"%23c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" opacity=\"0.3\"/><line x1=\"10\" y1=\"70\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"90\" stroke=\"%23c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" opacity=\"0.3\"/><line x1=\"90\" y1=\"70\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"90\" stroke=\"%23c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" opacity=\"0.3\"/><line x1=\"50\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"50\" y2=\"70\" stroke=\"%23c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" opacity=\"0.3\"/></svg>') no-repeat center center;\n            background-size: cover;\n            z-index: -1;\n            opacity: 0.5;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Secure Design Agency</h1>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n    <main>\n        <section class=\"hero-section\">\n            Crafting Your Vision, Securely.\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\" class=\"services-section\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\u2022 UI/UX Design</div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\u2022 Web Development</div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\u2022 Brand Identity</div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\u2022 Secure Solutions</div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-section\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>We ensure every project is built with security and integrity in mind.</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:contact@secure-design.com\">contact@secure-design.com</a></p>\n            <p>Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567</p>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n        &copy; 2023 Secure Design Agency. All rights reserved.\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}